is completely destroyed: the model misclassifies the vast majority of both
REAL and FAKE images, reducing accuracy to 6.14\%. The near-symmetry of
the adversarial matrix is consistent with the untargeted nature of FGSM,
which maximises loss without directing predictions toward a specific wrong
